node.text:
I don’t usually do mixers but… 

Pina Me Crazy

2 oz Tequila @tequilacurado 
2oz Pina Colada Mix @craftedbrandco 
.25oz Asian Pear Shrub @craftedbrandco 
.5oz Lime Juice

Method

Add all ingredients to an iced shaker. Shake and pour.
Garnish with a banana slice

Cheers!

Glassware @riedel_official

node.text:
This should be the motto of any bar or restaurant. Part of our job as service employees is making someone feel at home, part of the family, all the things. 

Once I’m established I’ll be announcing my new position. You guys have made me feel like I have a family… it may be online but that is not to be discounted. I appreciate every single person on here and I love y’all so much! 

#bartender #denver #denverbartender #barfam #bar
